title: Episode Two: James Roday Rodriguez - Spellingg Bee
description:
We're back baby! Another episode down in the books. This week, we have the ever-so-talented, star of the show, glue that held (and still holds) everyone together, James Roday Rodriguez.

We talk about his journey on how he became Shawn Spencer, how he almost gave up TV acting, and how he coined Tim's chest hair nickname, The Stern Bush.
